                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Chargé <persName type="to">Sleeper</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-07-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 20, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Bacon instructs the legation to make immediate inquiry into and send a full
                    report of an outrage which, as represented to President, has been committed in
                    the arrest of Miss Millie Brown, Lou Giltner, and young Augustine, Isle of
                    Pines.)</p>
            </div>
